


                                Angular -( localhost:4200 )
{
    project creation: syntax: ng new projec_name --routing

    project run: syntax: ng serve --open

    Component creation: syntax: ng g c Component_name

    service creation: syntax: ng g s service_name



}


             1. Component - { html, css, ts}- Root Component - AppComponent

             2. Module - Root Module - AppModule

             3. Data Binding

                3.1 One way Binding - data flow in 1 direction

                    3.1.1 From Component to View 

                        3.1.1.1 String Interpolation / Interpolation  - syntax: {{expression}}

                        3.1.1.2 Property Binding - syntax: [binding-target] ="binding-source"

                    3.1.2 From View to Component

                        3.1.2.1 Event Binding - syntax: (event)="function-call"

                        3.1.2.2 Event Binding using $event - syntax: (event)="function-call($event)"

                        3.1.2.3 Template referencing variable - syntax: #variable_name

                3.2 Two way Binding - data flow in 2 direction( ngModel - FormsModule ) syntax: [(ngModel)]="variable_name"
                        if ngModel in form tag then set name Property


